on his body?

884
00:31:18,076 --> 00:31:19,310
Didn't the police already ask?

885
00:31:19,811 --> 00:31:20,511
I don't know.

886
00:31:21,679 --> 00:31:22,313
Besides,

887
00:31:23,047 --> 00:31:24,315
what do those skin injuries

888
00:31:24,315 --> 00:31:25,283
have to do with his heart?

889
00:31:25,583 --> 00:31:26,284
Let's discuss the real issue.

890
00:31:26,651 --> 00:31:27,385
What exactly

891
00:31:27,452 --> 00:31:28,486
can be done for my child's heart?

892
00:31:33,958 --> 00:31:34,826
As I just said,

893
00:31:35,960 --> 00:31:36,894
with class IV heart failure,

894
00:31:37,595 --> 00:31:39,030
we need to consider a heart transplant.

895
00:31:39,964 --> 00:31:41,366
If you don't object,

896
00:31:41,933 --> 00:31:42,567
we'll register him

897
00:31:42,567 --> 00:31:43,468
in the system

898
00:31:43,735 --> 00:31:44,869
to wait for a donor heart.

899
00:31:48,473 --> 00:31:49,307
Replace his heart?

900
00:31:52,043 --> 00:31:53,211
Is it really that serious?

901
00:31:53,645 --> 00:31:54,012
Yes.

902
00:31:55,313 --> 00:31:56,014
Very serious.

903
00:31:57,448 --> 00:31:58,316
He's at risk

904
00:31:58,416 --> 00:31:59,284
of sudden death at any time.

905
00:31:59,550 --> 00:32:01,519
Doctor, is there any way

906
00:32:01,586 --> 00:32:04,656
to get a heart sooner?

907
00:32:04,756 --> 00:32:05,790
He's our only child.

908
00:32:06,124 --> 00:32:06,924
Even if I have to sell everything,

909
00:32:06,924 --> 00:32:08,426
I'll save him.

910
00:32:08,826 --> 00:32:09,427
Please.

911
00:32:09,961 --> 00:32:11,562
Help us with the donor somehow.

912
00:32:13,031 --> 00:32:14,399
Donors are allocated through the system.

913
00:32:15,133 --> 00:32:16,134
There is no way to arrange one privately.

914
00:32:18,269 --> 00:32:19,304
Use my heart.

915
00:32:19,404 --> 00:32:20,438
Give it to my son.

916
00:32:20,772 --> 00:32:21,706
Give him my heart.

917
00:32:22,907 --> 00:32:24,909
My child is still so young.

918
00:32:25,009 --> 00:32:27,045
He still has his whole life ahead of him.

919
00:32:28,012 --> 00:32:29,080
I understand how you feel,

920
00:32:29,547 --> 00:32:30,515
but that isn't realistic.

921
00:32:31,015 --> 00:32:32,283
Still, you don't need to panic.

922
00:32:32,450 --> 00:32:33,951
Before a donor heart becomes available,

923
00:32:34,152 --> 00:32:35,253
there is a bridge option.

924
00:32:36,087 --> 00:32:36,854
We can implant

925
00:32:36,854 --> 00:32:37,655
an artificial heart,

926
00:32:38,456 --> 00:32:39,324
a mechanical device

927
00:32:39,357 --> 00:32:40,692
to support his cardiac function.

928
00:32:41,626 --> 00:32:42,293
Do it. Do it.

929
00:32:43,761 --> 00:32:44,228
But I still need

930
00:32:44,228 --> 00:32:45,063
to remind you

931
00:32:46,064 --> 00:32:47,165
that an artificial heart is expensive.

932
00:32:47,865 --> 00:32:48,866
It costs several hundred thousand yuan.

933
00:32:50,268 --> 00:32:51,469
I'll find the money.

934
00:33:39,784 --> 00:33:40,351
Dr. Fang.

935
00:33:43,688 --> 00:33:44,122
What is it?

936
00:33:44,889 --> 00:33:46,424
Can I have my phone back?

937
00:33:47,959 --> 00:33:48,559
Your phone is with

938
00:33:48,559 --> 00:33:49,494
your parents.

939
00:33:51,429 --> 00:33:52,930
Then can I borrow

940
00:33:52,964 --> 00:33:53,765
your phone?

941
00:33:54,932 --> 00:33:56,200
I just want to make a call.

942
00:33:57,335 --> 00:33:57,668
Okay.

943
00:34:01,873 --> 00:34:02,306
Thank you.

944
00:34:12,750 --> 00:34:13,985
Hello? Who is this?

945
00:34:15,086 --> 00:34:15,720
Sanshui.

946
00:34:16,687 --> 00:34:17,388
It's me.

947
00:34:18,089 --> 00:34:18,790
Dahuo.

948
00:34:19,624 --> 00:34:20,625
Where have you been these past two days?

949
00:34:21,125 --> 00:34:22,493
Your phone has been off.

950
00:34:24,495 --> 00:34:25,329
I'm in the hospital.

951
00:34:35,873 --> 00:34:37,909
Brother Yi, have you decided?

952
00:34:38,443 --> 00:34:39,243
My birthday is next month.

953
00:34:39,310 --> 00:34:40,011
What are you getting me?

954
00:34:56,961 --> 00:34:57,428
You're done.

955
00:34:57,795 --> 00:34:58,196
Let's go.

956
00:35:01,466 --> 00:35:02,166
It's windy today.

957
00:35:05,436 --> 00:35:06,471
Do you have many surgeries today?

958
00:35:08,439 --> 00:35:08,973
About the usual.

959
00:35:10,041 --> 00:35:10,508
Okay.

960
00:35:11,108 --> 00:35:12,043
We'll see

961
00:35:12,043 --> 00:35:13,211
whether to have dinner together tonight.

962
00:35:24,522 --> 00:35:25,123
Why are you here?

963
00:35:25,590 --> 00:35:26,591
How did you know we were here?

964
00:35:27,725 --> 00:35:28,226
Uncle. Auntie.

965
00:35:28,993 --> 00:35:29,794
Du Yan called me

966
00:35:29,794 --> 00:35:30,628
and said he was hospitalized.

967
00:35:31,229 --> 00:35:32,363
I just wanted to see him.

968
00:35:32,430 --> 00:35:33,397
I'll say a few words and leave.

969
00:35:33,831 --> 00:35:34,365
See him for what?

970
00:35:34,966 --> 00:35:35,733
Stay away from our Du Yan.

971
00:35:36,000 --> 00:35:36,400
Go.

972
00:35:37,201 --> 00:35:38,569
I changed buses three times

973
00:35:38,769 --> 00:35:39,470
and spent over two hours

974
00:35:39,470 --> 00:35:40,004
getting here.

975
00:35:40,238 --> 00:35:41,239
He doesn't need you to visit.

976
00:35:41,472 --> 00:35:42,206
Go, go.

977
00:35:43,441 --> 00:35:44,175
Who is this?

978
00:35:44,442 --> 00:35:45,243
A classmate. We don't know him.

979
00:35:47,612 --> 00:35:48,012
Doctor.

980
00:35:48,212 --> 00:35:48,946
I'm Du Yan's friend.

981
00:35:49,814 --> 00:35:51,048
He called and said he was sick.

982
00:35:51,549 --> 00:35:52,550
I just want to see him.

983
00:35:53,317 --> 00:35:53,885
I promise I won't

984
00:35:53,885 --> 00:35:54,552
cause any trouble.

985
00:35:56,921 --> 00:35:58,623
Since Du Yan contacted him himself,

986
00:35:59,190 --> 00:36:00,591
seeing a good friend

987
00:36:00,758 --> 00:36:02,126
may improve his condition.

988
00:36:02,693 --> 00:36:03,528
Doctor, you don't know.

989
00:36:03,561 --> 00:36:04,095
Back then, they...

990
00:36:18,676 --> 00:36:19,644
I'll take him in first.

991
00:36:21,412 --> 00:36:21,879
Come with me.

992
00:36:24,882 --> 00:36:25,983
I'll transfer Yan Yan's surgical fees

993
00:36:26,751 --> 00:36:28,452
to you this afternoon.

994
00:36:28,886 --> 00:36:29,353
Thank you, Dad.

995
00:36:30,955 --> 00:36:32,023
Your mother and I

996
00:36:32,590 --> 00:36:34,025
only have this funeral money left.

997
00:36:34,325 --> 00:36:35,793
Now it's all going to you.

998
00:36:36,694 --> 00:36:37,929
Look at you.

999
00:36:38,396 --> 00:36:39,330
You're already middle-aged,

1000
00:36:39,530 --> 00:36:40,364
yet you're useless at everything.

1001
00:36:41,065 --> 00:36:41,966
You can't even

1002
00:36:41,999 --> 00:36:42,934
raise one child properly.

1003
00:36:43,367 --> 00:36:43,968
Your mother and I

1004
00:36:43,968 --> 00:36:45,036
raised four children

1005
00:36:45,036 --> 00:36:46,003
without this much trouble.

1006
00:36:46,771 --> 00:36:47,805
Look at yourself.

1007
00:36:48,506 --> 00:36:50,041
When something happens, you still beg your parents.

1008
00:36:50,107 --> 00:36:50,908
What use are you?

1009
00:36:51,075 --> 00:36:52,210
You're completely worthless.

1010
00:36:52,944 --> 00:36:53,477
How did the Du family

1011
00:36:53,511 --> 00:36:55,146
end up with a failure like you?

1012
00:36:55,413 --> 00:36:56,647
Think about it carefully.

1013
00:37:11,395 --> 00:37:11,829
Come in.

1014
00:37:19,003 --> 00:37:19,503
Sanshui.

1015
00:37:20,004 --> 00:37:20,404
Dahuo.

1016
00:37:23,507 --> 00:37:24,842
How did you end up like this?

1017
00:37:26,077 --> 00:37:26,677
It's nothing.

1018
00:37:27,712 --> 00:37:28,512
I fell.

1019
00:37:30,348 --> 00:37:31,682
It's your heart problem.

1020
00:37:46,931 --> 00:37:48,232
Dr. Xiaoran, look here.

1021
00:37:48,399 --> 00:37:49,166
Sign here.

1022
00:37:49,934 --> 00:37:50,768
I didn't know

1023
00:37:50,801 --> 00:37:51,669
you couldn't bring things inside.

1024
00:37:52,103 --> 00:37:53,237
I prepared a birthday gift for you.

1025
00:37:54,472 --> 00:37:55,039
They took it.

1026
00:37:56,040 --> 00:37:56,607
You can see it

1027
00:37:57,041 --> 00:37:57,675
after you recover and leave.

1028
00:37:58,509 --> 00:37:59,043
It's okay.

1029
00:38:00,344 --> 00:38:01,212
I don't need a birthday.

1030
00:38:02,346 --> 00:38:03,514
It's enough that you came.

1031
00:38:04,282 --> 00:38:04,749
But

1032
00:38:06,884 --> 00:38:08,152
clever and resourceful as I am,

1033
00:38:08,252 --> 00:38:08,986
I downloaded

1034
00:38:08,986 --> 00:38:09,720
this week's update in advance.

1035
00:38:12,023 --> 00:38:12,490
Come on.

1036
00:38:20,464 --> 00:38:20,831
Move closer.

1037
00:38:24,001 --> 00:38:24,335
Here.

1038
00:38:40,151 --> 00:38:41,519
So it's his birthday today.

1039
00:38:42,720 --> 00:38:44,622
Then he's turning eighteen.

1040
00:38:44,989 --> 00:38:45,790
His coming-of-age birthday.

1041
00:38:46,757 --> 00:38:48,292
That poor kid.

1042
00:38:49,527 --> 00:38:50,995
Fortunately, his good friend

1043
00:38:50,995 --> 00:38:51,562
came to keep him company.

1044
00:38:51,829 --> 00:38:53,130
Look. He's doing much better.

1045
00:38:53,264 --> 00:38:53,931
He's even smiling.

1046
00:39:55,393 --> 00:39:56,327
I never expected

1047
00:39:57,361 --> 00:39:59,029
the story to develop like this.

1048
00:39:59,530 --> 00:40:00,431
We'll wait for next week's update.

1049
00:40:02,733 --> 00:40:03,033
Right.

1050
00:40:04,869 --> 00:40:05,336
There's also this.

1051
00:40:06,904 --> 00:40:07,705
On your eighteenth birthday,

1052
00:40:10,107 --> 00:40:11,475
you have to make a wish and blow out candles.

1053
00:40:13,611 --> 00:40:14,078
Make a wish.

1054
00:40:32,296 --> 00:40:32,630
Blow.

1055
00:40:39,303 --> 00:40:39,770
Pretty cool, right?

1056
00:40:42,873 --> 00:40:43,908
What a good friend.

1057
00:40:52,583 --> 00:40:53,117
The doctor said

1058
00:40:53,184 --> 00:40:54,251
I'm already a special exception.

1059
00:40:54,752 --> 00:40:55,719
I can only stay for half an hour.

1060
00:41:00,157 --> 00:41:00,758
So I'll go now.

1061
00:41:02,827 --> 00:41:03,360
Happy birthday.

1062
00:42:02,753 --> 00:42:03,921
Happy birthday.

1063
00:42:05,756 --> 00:42:06,557
I only just found out

1064
00:42:06,557 --> 00:42:07,691
today is your birthday.

1065
00:42:07,758 --> 00:42:08,692
I had to prepare this in a hurry.

1066
00:42:09,393 --> 00:42:10,160
It's just a small gift.

1067
00:42:13,664 --> 00:42:15,399
You've been eating bland food for days.

1068
00:42:15,566 --> 00:42:16,367
You must be craving something tasty.

1069
00:42:17,368 --> 00:42:18,202
When you're better,

1070
00:42:18,502 --> 00:42:19,970
I'll take you to our cafeteria for a feast.

1071
00:42:20,604 --> 00:42:21,071
Thank you.

1072
00:42:23,173 --> 00:42:24,208
I have a good friend

1073
00:42:24,575 --> 00:42:25,676
whose birthday is also today.

1074
00:42:26,744 --> 00:42:27,745
He's two years older than you.

1075
00:42:28,545 --> 00:42:30,047
Today would be his twentieth birthday.

1076
00:42:30,548 --> 00:42:32,116
He liked flowers and plants.

1077
00:42:32,516 --> 00:42:33,517
He liked making things by hand.

1078
00:42:34,718 --> 00:42:34,952
Oh, right.

1079
00:42:35,185 --> 00:42:35,886
Just like you,

1080
00:42:36,053 --> 00:42:37,454
he had lots of badges hanging from his bag.

1081
00:42:38,222 --> 00:42:38,689
Really?

1082
00:42:39,823 --> 00:42:41,492
But he probably isn't like me,

1083
00:42:42,326 --> 00:42:43,327
spending his birthday in a hospital.

1084
00:42:48,866 --> 00:42:50,134
He's somewhere else,

1085
00:42:52,870 --> 00:42:54,004
together with his father.
